title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

Does anyone have plans for building a bat house that you'd be willing to share with me? [From a letter in the March 2004 issue of Country Extra. Submitted by Harriet Rosenberg, Danbury, Connecticut.]
